name: Chicken Enchilada Soup
ingredients: 1 lb chicken breast diced/cooked 1 cup enchilada sauce (﴾red)﴿
1/2 cup diced onion 16 oz. velveeta cheese
4 cups of chicken broth 1 tsp chili powder
1 cup of mexican corn flour 1/2 tsp cumin
steps: Cook chicken and onions. Add water, broth and flour. Whisk add rest of ingredients and heat through.
